remaining_laws3 <- c("(3-501.16) POTENTIALLY HAZARDOUS shall be maintained: (1) At 57�C (135�F) or above, except that roasts cooked to a temperature and for a time specified under � 3-401.11(B) or reheated as specified in � 3-403.11(E) may be held at a temperature of 54�C (130�F) or above",
